    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">This is an optional class feature. Consult with your DM before adding this to your character.</em></p>\n<p>At 2nd level, you can expend a use of your @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.idX3IP3WYFKhjm8g]{Channel Divinity} to fuel your spells. As a bonus action, you touch your holy symbol, utter a prayer, and regain <strong>one expended spell slot</strong>, the level of which can be no higher than <strong>half your proficiency bonus</strong> (rounded up).</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Channel Divinity.</em></p>\n</section>",
